{"tid":1831131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又係食環］放蛇告黃店維園花檔買花無收佢5毫子膠袋徵費 要票控看檔青年","createTime":"2020-01-20T07:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T13:00:46.000Z","uid":22556,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"edbc46c81cbfcd8a2e7856cc27512ad8322062be","tid":1831131,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D56LiVS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD56LiVS.jpg&h=c7a869a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【網友分享】// 剛剛經過維園年宵49 遍地開花，有環保署職員放蛇買花，一男一女，各五十幾歲，聲稱女職員沒有收膠袋徵費，不斷恐女職員要抄佢身份證，票控佢！當時負責人不在，只有年青既男職員同女職員，環保署職員聲稱不提交身分證就報警，搵警察處理，年青職員不知所措！<br />\n<br />\n成個維園咁多間花店，環保署職員係要捉呢間，我就唔信旺角花墟同全港咁多間花舖都有收膠袋徵費！我打過去環保署，佢地都話係票控舖頭，唔係票控員工！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n支持黃店！//"},{"pid":"0d6420458b5911bf3158c327b79a46b0fddcab41","tid":1831131,"uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2722801197806686/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F178965725523592%2Fposts%2F2722801197806686%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV99qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=8ff26bd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2722801197806686/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"1273417792d2aff1bf074ea1332ac25618e2cc03","tid":1831131,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>港共清算進行中</strong>"},{"pid":"d27c20f4c84aca08fdf152767f066ed36a63f7db","tid":1831131,"uid":76776,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:23:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ec3f53f6198543e6e597990cf97e3196b648f40","tid":1831131,"uid":24853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:24:47.000Z","msg":"投訴哂所有藍店無收膠袋費"},{"pid":"18dcde0fc2533670860e587d1c256969024c6ec6","tid":1831131,"uid":37869,"like":1,"d